ROC1AUD.original: ~z~is the Russian has come to Mr. Ancelotti and said he wants the head of anyone involved with the diamonds.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~俄国人来找Ancelotti先生了，他说要干掉所有跟钻石有关联的人。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~But I may be about to kill you two fucks though.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~但我说不定会杀掉你们两个混蛋。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Think about it, I'll be in touch.
~z~One of us goes out, we both go out.
~z~Okay, boss. I'll be in the security room if you need me.
~z~I don't know! Didn't he say the Russians are coming?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~不知道！他是不是说俄国人要过来了？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Ouch. The terrible irony. You better tell him.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~天啊，太可笑了。你跟他直说吧。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Do you know how much that paintwork cost, you assholes?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~知道那幅画值多少钱吗，一帮傻蛋？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~D, what's happening? You're fucking kidding me. Get out of here.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~D，怎么了？别他妈开玩笑了，从店里出去。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You tried to kill me, Lou. You wanted to fucking kill me!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~你刚才想杀我，Lou。你他妈居然想杀了我！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Think about it. I'll be in touch... you fuckin spic.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~好好想想吧，我们再联系...傻逼西班牙佬。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~That's what I told them. That shit would have never happened back in the day.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~我就是这么说的，以前绝对不会有这种事。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Use that shit, man. That's gonna help you survive.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~利用好状态，哥们。这样才能活下来。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Shit. Shit. Shit. Can you get rid of these badly dressed pricks?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，妈的，妈的。能不能干掉这帮衣冠不整的混蛋？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Me and Vince would prefer to work with you in the clubs, over the faggot, so you're lucky.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~我跟Vince更希望和你经营夜店，而不是那个基佬，算你走运。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Well, I guess it was never gonna be easy, was it? Let's go see what's happening.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，确实不会那么简单，对吧？先上了再说吧。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Refurb. Rebrand. I'm an earner. I'm a survivor.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~翻修，重塑品牌。我成功过，笑到了最后。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Thank god you got here, Luis. These fucking guys...
~z~Whatever. It don't matter, alright, what matters...
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~无所谓了。这不重要好吧，重要的是...

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Stuff's got weird with Tony, Dess. There's some really bad shit that might be about to happen in there.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~Tony现在处境不妙，Dess。店里可能会出大麻烦。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~A whole lot more of them are arriving outside.
~z~I don't know. I guess he was committed to the job. This doesn't change the fact that we're fucked, Lou.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~不知道啊，可能他太爱这份工作了吧。但这无法改变我们完蛋了的事实，Lou。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~There's another Russian army arriving outside the club, and I don't think any of them are planning on paying for bottle service.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~点外面又来了一群俄国佬，我看他们都不是来喝酒的。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Yo, boss! I think we clear out here. Come out.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~呦，老板！感觉我们安全了。出来吧。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Are you joking? More of these bastards?
~z~Your brand of charming homosexuality, it's kind of run out of steam.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~你招牌的男同魅力，现在不太顶用了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I been pushed to the brink, Lou. I'm over the fucking edge.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~我快顶不住了，Lou。我他妈要崩溃了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~He's making a run for the VIP area. Check behind us, Lou.
~z~Well, you did bring the heat down on the club, so...I can understand why they blame you.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~那你确实把火引到了我们夜店...他们怪你我也可以理解。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Sure it is. We got money coming. We can expand.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~当然很简单。我们还有存款，可以再扩张。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Keep your head, Lou. He's a made guy.
~z~You want bodies, we give you fuckin' bodies.
~z~you was family, man. But it's either you, or all of us.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~你是我的家人，哥们。但现在要么你死，要么大家一起死。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~This is for the Old Man and that's it.
~z~Luis! I just got a call from Dessie. He's says they've sent another wave. They're arriving outside the club.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~Luis！我接到了Dessie的电话。他说又来了一波敌人，马上就要到店门口了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Alright? So basically, it's you or Tony.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~好吗？简单来说，要么是你，要么是Tony。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I was here before you Russian bastards, and I'll be here after you.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~今天我就要和你们这帮俄国佬做个了断，一定是我的胜利。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~If it wasn't them trying to kill us, someone else would be.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~就算他们不来袭击，也会有别人。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You motherfucking bitch mother fucking fuck fuckers!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~这帮狗娘他妈养的他妈的他妈混蛋！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You know, Mr. Ancellotti's still blaming all that diamond shit for Gracie's kidnap.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~知道吗，Ancelotti先生仍然认为是钻石导致的Gracie被绑架。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Shit! Dessie just called me. A whole lot more of them are arriving outside.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的！Dessie打电话给我了。外面来了更多敌人。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Why was Dessie even here? The clubs were shut down.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~为什么Dessie还在这儿？店不是被关了吗。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Having a moment of genuine fucking clarity.
~z~The Russians are coming, man. We don't got time for this gay shit.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~俄国人就要来了，哥们。别搁这儿演肥皂剧了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~or the Russian is gonna send some serious people around to wack you and the fag...
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~Ancelotti就会同意俄国佬派杀手追杀你和基佬...

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Nice one, Lou. Nice. We're marked men now.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~很好，Lou。很好。我们现在跑不掉了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Fucking shit up? Really, bro? I was trying to save your ass. Enjoy fending for yourself, okay?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~我搞砸了？你确定，老兄？我是想救你啊。要么你自己保护自己？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Perfect. More goons to ruin my club!
~z~They didn't give us a second, did they? Shit!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~喘口气的机会都没有啊？妈的！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Talk to them. Tell them we can figure it out.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~跟他们谈谈。告诉他们会有办法的。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You want us dead, you fucking try it in here.
~z~I bet you wished you killed me now, Lou.
~z~I'll die in the club I built.
~z~I think they're getting up the stairs. Look out!
~z~the Old Man, you're fucking dead, the both of you.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~还有老头子。你俩死定了，谁都跑不了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Don't be stupid, T. T, please don't be stupid. I'll just come find you. Shit.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~别犯傻，T。T，千万别犯傻。我会来找你的。妈的。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You come into my club and do this?
~z~Get out my club, you fucking mook!
~z~They're coming up the stairs. They'll get behind us!
~z~You didn't tell me there were this many, Luis!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~你可没告诉我会有这么多人，Luis！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~you get to keep the clubs, you and us together, partners.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~夜店都归你管。你和我们一起，合伙经营。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Laying low, boss. This ain't his fight.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~他躲着呢，老板。这事与他无关。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Fuck, Dessie. You serious? Get the fuck out of here. Thank you.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Dessie。没搞错吧？你他妈赶紧跑吧。谢谢。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~And you? You're a fucking loser, hanging out with children living a fantasy life.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~还有你，就一个窝囊废，整天和小屁孩一起做白日梦。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You ain't getting shot in here, T, you melodramatic asshole.
~z~There's Russians, fucking everyone, they're coming after you,
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~会有俄国人，他妈的各种人，都会来追杀你。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Oh shit! How many of these guys are there?
~z~Look at him. Charging in there and everything fucking up.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~看看他。掌管着一切，搞砸了一切。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I'll be no good to you out there. Come on.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~我在外面只会拖累你。你上吧。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You seriously think you can step foot in our club and take us down?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~你们真以为闯进我们的店还能干掉我们？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I'm packing up and I'm leaving town. I'm heading to a spa town in the desert. It's been nice knowing you.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~我要收拾东西，离开这里。我去沙漠里的绿洲避难了。很高兴认识你。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Fuck boss, you alright? There a whole load more guys showing up.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的老板，你还好吗？外面又来了一批人。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Are you sure not shooting me was smart? I don't think so...
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~没杀了我就很明智吗？我不这么想...

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~And those chinks they're still fucking pissed at that dispute of ours.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~那帮中国佬也气不过上次跟我们的冲突。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I'm sorry for bringing these Russians into this, T.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~把这些俄国人卷进来我真的很抱歉，T。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~He's got a fucking army! There's more of them here!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~他的手下太多了吧！更多人涌进来了！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Who'd we beat? A couple of goons? The guys who wanted us dead are still out there! I'm done.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~打败谁了？一群傻子吗？想干掉我们的人都还活着呢！我死定了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I guess we got to fight out way out then. Come on!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~那我们得杀出一条血路了！走吧！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~They're coming any second and they're expecting corpses.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~他们随时会发动袭击，不死不休。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You're the last Russian gangster we letting in here.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~以后不会再有俄国黑帮进店了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Any of them come through here, I'll have your back covered.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~有人从后面过来的话，我会保护好你的。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~We fucked up your boys, we'll fuck you up too.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~我们干掉了你的手下，我们还要干掉你。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~How many people are gonna try to kill me in one fucking day?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~今天到底有多少人想干掉我？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~ Ah...alright, if we're gonna operate we're gonna need some - some goodwill here.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~ 啊...好吧，要是还想开店，就得和气生财。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Dess, that you? Oh shit. Run. For God's sake, run while you still can!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~Dess，是你吗？哦妈的。快跑。看在上帝的份上，能跑多远就跑多远！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You're way out of your league kid.
~z~Then we gonna have to go meet 'em, boss. It's got to end sometime.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~那得去会会他们了，老板。迟早要解决的。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You the best Bulgarin can afford, you pussies?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~你们就是Bulgarin最好的手下，一帮怂包？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I'll get massacred if I walk out there.
~z~Rocco wasn't bullshitting about the Russian hit squad!
~z~You and your family and those spic drug dealers you hang out with.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~你，你的家人，还有跟你混在一起的那帮西班牙毒贩子，

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Someone has to pay for what's gone down.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~得有人为之前的事付出代价。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~You fucking kidding me? Even more of them?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~这他妈是开玩笑吗？又来这么多人？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Must have been the first time in his life he wasn't talking shit!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~他这辈子估计就说了这一句实话！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Lou. I'm not built to handle these fucks.
~z~Then we gonna have to go meet 'em, boss. It's got to end sometime.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~那我们得去会会他们了，老板。迟早要了结的。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Oh, you assholes! And I mean that.
~z~These guys, man, these fucking guys! You never should have brought them in, man.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~这帮人，哥们，这帮鸟人！你就不应该把他们卷进来，哥们。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Now, on top of all that Gracie and chink shit, the Old Man is pissed. He wants blood.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~再加上Gracie和中国佬的事，老头子也生气了。他要见血。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Tony, man, what the fuck? We got through it. We beat them.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~Tony，哥们，什么情况？我们成功了，打败他们了。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I can't go out there. Get rid of them, Lou.
~z~Tell your boss to settle this in person.
~z~This ain't nothing to do with you. You've seen nothing and heard nothing.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~这事跟你一点关系都没有。你什么都没看到，也什么都没听到。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Not in my VIP area, you cocks! Look behind us!
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~别搞烂我的贵宾区，混蛋！当心背后！

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~I think we can cut a deal - we give him one body.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~但还有回旋余地：我们交一个人出去。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~Come on, bitches. You want to step to this?
~z~What's up, ladies? Still living the high life, I see?
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~你们好吗，女士们？小日子过得还滋润吗？

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~He sent more guys? What a fucking idiot. Killing him will be fun.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~他又派了一批人？真他妈是个白痴。期待杀了他的那天。

ROC1AUD.original: ~z~We're okay here. You need to get out of here though.
ROC1AUD.translated: ~z~我们没问题的。你还是赶紧跑吧。
